msg: Added automatic multiPart support to fix bug#1255297.  You can still call Form.setMultiPart, but it is no longer necessary.

author: jonl
msg: Moved setParameters call inside null check block.  Improved comments.  Added check for !isCacheable() that bypasses getResourceStream() if the Resource is not cacheable.

msg: Added support for parameterized Resources via getParameters() and setParameters() as discussed on wicket-user.  Also, sorted members and formatted code.
